Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:28.56,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朱門帝子綻群芳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:36.81,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忍送百千神女去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:46.67,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1200)}但見高閣燈影長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:13.55,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}歸途應過出雲道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:25.67,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}神樂銀鈴綴良宵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:34.69,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}鈴音盡處見浮島
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:44.07,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1200)}島中燭火影飄搖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:58.56,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}暫上霧舟臨天際
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:10.88,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同心共禱干戈息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:19.42,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}歲月翔集歌聲起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:28.92,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1200)}雲海長燈影迷離
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:43.34,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}懷抱湧水明天光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:55.71,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}神月驅暗愛語揚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:04:04.24,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}更有狐仙同前路
