Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊  有那麼多人都趕到湯乃鷺來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為縣外也有人過來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.49,0:00:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  許願板
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  大家可都拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（存錢）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多東西  不覺得放棄還太早了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我現在到湯乃鷺了）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我去接下阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要我開車送你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  你們先去雪願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子  真是個靜不下來的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她這麼跑掉好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啥關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你寫了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.74,0:01:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成為新幹線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說我可是很現實的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一個反面教材生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣  不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anything  去那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢…可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是say anything的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是告訴過你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  媽媽  給我買蘋果糖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你開什麼玩笑  要買自己買
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真小氣  跟緒花一個樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 是她像我才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要五百萬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓腳踝瘦下來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家只是在把煩惱發洩出來而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做偷窺別人願望這樣惡趣味的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我想成為四十萬翠  緒花）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像老闆娘那樣  對工作充滿自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處事態度認真  卻有些孩子氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時都不曾忘記自己最初的那份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曾忘記最早的那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成為這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個夢想  不是我一個人就能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是因為有許多人的雪願照亮了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  輸掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過正是因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才必須雪願才行  在各種方面上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪願？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花她不是說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪願嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你寫什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看一下下沒關係啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很棒哦  小民
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:03:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啦行啦鶴來同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不會少你一塊肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要什麼緊要什麼緊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（希望我有朝一日能夠趕上徹先生  民子）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（作為一名廚師  希望能夠更上一層樓  徹）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不跑得再快些  可是趕不上我的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…你來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合身哦  女服務員的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃炒麵！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  來一份炒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:04:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須好好說出來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路邊攤的炒麵給人一種特別的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常在店裡吃的還有家裡做的都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也喜歡路邊攤的炒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡…阿孝！  非常喜歡！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場祭典能把所有的願望帶往天上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你離開以後  我本打算一個人繼續往前衝的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個以我為夢想的外孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話我想再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再一次…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我要到兒子那邊去住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我守在鍋爐前  不意間已經過了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多我也該準備後事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這兒積累起來的重要回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算一個不漏地全帶到棺材裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我由衷地感謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向老闆娘說一聲謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和孫子幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽  我說兩句可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家也都能聽一聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的事讓我明白了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還遠遠不夠老練
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說媽了  就連姐姐我都趕不上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法子咯  天生才能就不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我說過希望大家能跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還不是這塊料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽  你要關喜翠莊這件事…我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過只是暫時關門而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我絕不會讓喜翠莊就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要多學習一些  多修煉一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有朝一日能夠讓旅館重新開業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到那個時候  再讓我繼承喜翠莊這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想開一家讓媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓老闆娘喜悅的旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺  到那時候我也會幫你一把的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮先生  我也一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣  丟下老公也要來這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是些笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}誒  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們越笨越可愛呢  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今晚就盡情喝吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一醉方休！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你也一塊喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有成年…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼  少裝可愛了  這小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不准長時間逗留哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想搞些什麼花樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可得乖乖給我打報告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去偷窺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽  你接下來打算怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想暫時在熟人家裡打擾一陣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟緒花一起來東京不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是打算留在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找一個能讓我做女服務員混口飯吃的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混口飯吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起指使別人  自己幹活更合我的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要雪願
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會繼續做一個討人厭的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝您  母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不行不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床單的這裡不折好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  在這麼破的房間裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還和一個有點古怪的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過居然是白住…總感覺挺過意不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人說我很少會邀朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個個都高興得莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間旅館果然超級棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅館也是  這裡工作的人也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你找到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得所謂的歸宿啊  並不是一開始就在那邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是要自己找到  自己做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你我不免這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…會找到的  我的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個歸宿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…我的…歸宿…跟你的一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼鬼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這裡是我的房間啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花的男朋友人好像很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  只不過優柔寡斷而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然輸給那種男人  徹先生真可憐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多事情不是輸贏能說清的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說的…也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒在老闆娘房間裡睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠莊裡我的歸宿是這裡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次搖熊鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個季節貌似熊會出沒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…便利商店好遠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞鎮一圈的睡衣祭還將繼續！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘了買肉包了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮過自己為什麼會那麼執著於喜翠莊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…能一直和徹先生在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:12:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那個沒錯…但才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…我的夢想…不知不覺間變了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前一心想著成為廚師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.63,0:13:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我想成為喜翠莊的廚師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民好厲害啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想什麼的…雖然還不是很清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我希望能再回到喜翠莊來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到這個許許多多的夢想誕生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想…誕生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以前就是在那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用以前這種過去時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那裡  一定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…在未來的某一天…就會在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠莊將作為湯乃鷺的歷史建築物保存下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向這段短暫的經歷告別
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向這段悠久的歷史告別
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松前同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會給你發郵件的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會去找你玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  小翠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是已經走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個  不小心沒趕上車
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離下班火車還有些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要好好道一聲別
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這裡…喜翠莊告別…一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘您知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊木板的紋理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼看都像是個人臉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊與其說是像人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次來到喜翠莊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得這就像是故事中登場的旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是不出意料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了許多故事般的趣事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都遇上不同的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這都是因為大家都在雪願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命努力的人聚集在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命雪願的話  當然會發生各種各樣的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫下故事的也正是大家一份一份的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以即使不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在哪裡  一定都能創造  故事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.47,0:18:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我會回到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候就由你來代替電六記錄這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎  讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意的話就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我…由我來代替豆丁老爺繼續記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本業務日誌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…一定會回到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會面總不能遲到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還一定只是花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.26,0:23:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…也正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能夠仰望高高在上的太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.87,0:23:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敞開喉嚨暢飲水分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.80,0:23:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正準備綻放呢
